docs.lead_paragraph: ROME, March 4. -- Probably there is not a business man anywhere the world who can look over the balance sheet of the Italian tobacco monopoly without feelings of envy Its net profits last year were about $130,000,000, representing more the 80 per cent of its total revenue which is considered the highest ratio of profit to revenue which can be shown by any industrial interprise of importance.

docs.lead_paragraph: REPRESENTING a further step in its original program of creating a national organization for the development of aeronautical and radio law and to advance scientific research and investigation in these fields, the American Academy of Air, founded by men connected with New York University School of Law, announced last week that Washington University School of Law at Seattle had become affiliated with it.
